# Customer API Release Rule

When the user asks to publish, package, archive, or create a release for the Customer API, read and follow `Customer/Api/Docs/CustomerApiPublishAndPackage.md`.

Use the `customer-api-release` skill. Do not clear `D:\Release` without explicit user authorization. Publish only with configuration `Release` and output `D:\Release`, then create and test `D:\Release\Release.rar`.
